{"tid":559381,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"MIUI 得票不敵 Android One 小米怒刪 Twitter 投票","createTime":"2018-02-13T06:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T01:31:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"947d537969cf60b02fb438c1028e346774f09e8c","tid":559381,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/0213-1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F0213-1b.jpg&h=98cf293b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以往一直以自家 MIUI 作為介面的小米，去年開始和 Google 合作，以對方的 Android One 作為小米 A1 的系統介面。小米 A1 採用原生 Android 系統成功吸引不少外國用戶捧場，早前小米的官方 Twitter 曾經舉行投票，讓網民選擇小米 MIUI 9 還是 Google 的 Android One。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n類似投票如果在大陸舉行，可能小米支持者會一窩蜂將票投予 MIUI，不過國際市場的用戶則傾向沒有任何添加，並且有更佳系統更新和升級支持的 Android One。投票結果顯示 Android One 一直都領先 MIUI 9，有外國網民認為小米無法接受這個結果，最後竟然在 24 小時內將投票從 Twitter 刪除，當作沒有發生過一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然小米嘗試「毀滅證據」，但還是有網民將投票結果截圖。在選舉舉行了不足 24小時，已經有接近 15,000 人投票，結果 MIUI 得票 43%，而 Android One 則得票 57%。<br />\n<br />\n來源：pocketnow"},{"pid":"b596218f85e5184a628516a301fed4dac8e81f16","tid":559381,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd929e5f1d9ed7fdf17ded20e4d74658d45b96d7","tid":559381,"uid":12628,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"竟然有43%人投屌米個垃圾rom, 執到啦"},{"pid":"a16478133317a8fc6bcdb203cbdad937983df0cb","tid":559381,"uid":15358,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dd929e5f1d9ed7fdf17ded20e4d74658d45b96d7","tid":559381,"uid":12628,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"竟然有43%人投屌米個垃圾rom, 執到啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"可能覺得43%太多 有人種票 <br />\n所以del post 一定係"},{"pid":"0379c898f773014a0233